snippet.title: Tails of Iron - Story Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Embark on an RPG adventure to save the rat kingdom from the Frog clan in Tails of Iron. This hand-drawn adventure is out in 2021 on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox.
